| Open state control            | `on_open_change` callback     | `open` / `defaultOpen` / `onOpenChange` | `open` / `defaultOpen` / `onOpenChange` | `isOpen` / `defaultOpen` / `onOpenChange` | ars-ui uses callback-only; open state is internal     |
