### 5.4 Features

| Feature              | ars-ui                   | Ark UI                  | Radix UI          | React Aria |
| -------------------- | ------------------------ | ----------------------- | ----------------- | ---------- |
| Single select        | Yes                      | Yes                     | Yes               | Yes        |
| Multi select         | Yes                      | Yes                     | --                | Yes        |
| Typeahead            | Yes                      | Yes                     | Yes               | Yes        |
| Disabled items       | Yes                      | Yes                     | Yes               | Yes        |
| Item groups          | Yes                      | Yes                     | Yes               | Yes        |
